20 shall not apply to claims from individuals not in the custody of the
21 Department of Corrections based on accidents involving motor
22 vehicles owned or operated by the Department of Corrections;
23 24. The activities of the state military forces when on state
24 active duty orders or on Title 32 active duty orders;
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - HB3581 SFLR Page 8
